sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Script as bootstrap-all.sh / run-bootstrap-job.sh
  participant Job as media-stack-bootstrap Job
  participant Apps as Arr + Prowlarr + Jellyseerr + qB

  User->>Script: Run bootstrap
  Script->>Script: Ensure qB secret/credentials
  Script->>Job: Apply ConfigMaps + launch job
  Job->>Apps: Wait for services
  Job->>Apps: Configure root folders
  Job->>Apps: Configure Prowlarr app links
  Job->>Apps: Configure qB categories/download clients
  Job->>Apps: Configure Jellyseerr Sonarr/Radarr
  Job->>Apps: Trigger Prowlarr indexer sync
  Script->>User: Show logs + completion
